---
title: BBQ-Seasoned Double Salmon with Red Onion and Apple Salad
description: BBQ spiced salmon tops this summer-inspired delight! Quick roasted sweet onions get tossed with slivers of crisp apples, toasted almonds and spring mix. A simple oil and vinegar dressing is all you need to bring this whole dish together.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bbq-seasoned-double-salmon-51e3153d.jpg
